      "seed": 1633723822,
      "version": 237,
      "versionNonce": 2043458990,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774591196700,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "- Weekly cron — fetches top-ranked products per genre from\nRakuten API\n\n- Normalize → price → upsert into PostgreSQL (skip if\nunchanged, update if price changed)\n\n- Push to WooCommerce via REST API\n\n- On-demand product request handler\n    keyword → fetch → normalize → price → store → push → \n    SSE progress stream to customer\n\n- Writes run logs and product stats to shared volume",
      "fontSize": 12.621719071168924,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "- Weekly cron — fetches top-ranked products per genre from Rakuten API\n\n- Normalize → price → upsert into PostgreSQL (skip if unchanged, update if price changed)\n\n- Push to WooCommerce via REST API\n\n- On-demand product request handler\n    keyword → fetch → normalize → price → store → push → \n    SSE progress stream to customer\n\n- Writes run logs and product stats to shared volume",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
