      "text": "Auth handling (4)\n\ndashboard renders screenshots from server and allows\noperator to scan QR code to sign in with phone\n\nPlaywright detects the login, saves auth.json and\ncloses the instance/stream\n\n",
      "fontSize": 10.663604572675935,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Auth handling (4)\n\ndashboard renders screenshots from server and allows operator to scan QR code to sign in with phone\n\nPlaywright detects the login, saves auth.json and closes the instance/stream\n\n",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
