      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1774591039151,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": " - change config to change Rakuten Container behavior\n    - edit margin %, shipping estimates, scrape       \n      schedule etc\n - allows monitoring/view of run log and state\n - allows viewing product stats ",
      "fontSize": 16.2973929827986,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": " - change config to change Rakuten Container behavior\n    - edit margin %, shipping estimates, scrape                 \n      schedule etc\n - allows monitoring/view of run log and state\n - allows viewing product stats ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "hpBlkFi6jTZTWGp5MQI8E",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4390.480349343416,
      "y": 41.916957137748284,
      "width": 519.3723955958089,
      "height": 102.51768462006224,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 0,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b3E",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1314365554,
      "version": 448,
      "versionNonce": 2082953586,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1774591033601,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "By calling Rakuten Express server :3002 for commands\n - allows fetch more products (with category/count input)\n - allows retry failed imports to Woocommerce\n - manually trigger a keyword trigger (test on-demand\nproduct request flow end-to end)",
      "fontSize": 16.402829539209957,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "By calling Rakuten Express server :3002 for commands\n - allows fetch more products (with category/count input)\n - allows retry failed imports to Woocommerce\n - manually trigger a keyword trigger (test on-demand product request flow end-to end)",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
